OL,3,C'Actor' who claimed to look like Brad
OL,4,CPitt jailed for rape and 'stealthing'
OL,6,FA self-proclaimed actor who believed
OL,7,Fhe resembled Brad Pitt has been jailed
OL,8,Ffor 16 years for a series of sexual
OL,9,Foffences, including rape for secretly
OL,10,Fnot using a condom.
OL,12,FLuke Ford, 35, from Stirling,
OL,13,FScotland, was convicted of 19 charges,
OL,14,Fincluding violence, sexual assault,
OL,15,Fthreats, and abuse against women.
OL,17,FOne of the seven rape charges against
OL,18,Fhim involved "stealthing," the act of
OL,19,Fremoving a condom without a partner's
OL,20,Fknowledge or consent.
