OL,4,CPitt jailed for rape and 'stealthing'
OL,6,FHe was found to have deliberately had
OL,7,Funprotected sex despite the woman only
OL,8,Fagreeing to sex with a condom.
OL,10,FFord was given a 21-year extended
OL,11,Fsentence with 16 years in custody at
OL,12,Fthe High Court in Edinburgh on
OL,13,FWednesday, the Crown Office said.
OL,15,FThe court heard how Ford targeted nine
OL,16,Ffemale victims over a 12-year campaign
OL,17,Fof abuse that lasted from 2008 to 2020.
