OL,6,FFord was described as a sporadic actor
OL,7,Fwho appeared in the music video for
OL,8,FDeacon Blue's This Is a Love Song. He
OL,9,Falso claimed to have served as a stand-
OL,10,Fin for Brad Pitt in the 2013 film
OL,11,FWorld War Z, which had some scenes
OL,12,Ffilmed in Glasgow.
OL,14,FAnother victim told the court she gave
OL,15,FFord a condom before sex, believing he
OL,16,Fhad used it. He later admitted he had
OL,17,Fnot, and told her to take the morning-
OL,18,Fafter pill or have an abortion if she
OL,19,Fbecame pregnant.
