OL,6,FKatrina Parkes, procurator fiscal for
OL,7,FHigh Court sexual offending, said:
OL,8,F"Luke Ford is a serial offender who
OL,9,Fdemonstrated no respect for the
OL,10,Fconsent of his victims.
OL,12,F"He was prepared to use manipulation,
OL,13,Fforce or threats to carry out his
OL,14,Fabuse. He showed disregard for the
OL,15,Fimportance of consent between partners.
OL,17,F"I would urge any victim of similar
OL,18,Foffending to take confidence from
OL,19,FFord's conviction. Please come
OL,20,Fforward, report your experience and
OL,21,Fseek help."
